    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. Meticulously maintained, the chassis exhibits zero subframe fatigue, and the ZF 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp, tactile engagement. The original Laguna Seca Blue finish remains in concours state, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating. Performance is bolstered by a factory-spec limited-slip differential and perfectly calibrated suspension geometry, ensuring the razor-sharp turn-in and linear power delivery these machines are famed for. A true collector-grade example with a documented service history that leaves no room for compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
